        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[失望]#胃不舒服不要总是忍和熬#】数据显示，慢性胃炎已成为我国最常见的上消化道疾病。饮食不规律、爱吃辛辣刺激食物、过量饮酒等不良饮食习惯，是导致胃黏膜...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[失望]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shiwang-b4bf17068f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%80%BB%E6%98%AF%E5%BF%8D%E5%92%8C%E7%86%AC%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E4%B8%8D%E8%88%92%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%80%BB%E6%98%AF%E5%BF%8D%E5%92%8C%E7%86%AC%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃不舒服不要总是忍和熬#</span></a>】数据显示，慢性胃炎已成为我国最常见的上消化道疾病。饮食不规律、爱吃辛辣刺激食物、过量饮酒等不良饮食习惯，是导致胃黏膜损伤的一大因素。此外，长期精神紧张、焦虑等<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%9D%8F%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%B9%9F%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%9D%8F%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%B9%9F%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#坏情绪也会伤胃#</span></a>。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D#%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%8A%A4%E8%83%83%E6%97%A5#&amp;extparam=#%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E6%8A%A4%E8%83%83%E6%97%A5#" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#今天国际护胃日#</span></a>，医生提醒：若胃部不适反复发作，用药后症状仍不缓解，务必及时就医，提防小病变大病！ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4888520331034654" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hct3x9oszhj61zw14g4qp02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/a6luoYUIlx084wvzu9BK01041200TyC80E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681118386&amp;ssig=wfhjSKRbxR&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XETzoOwDlx084wvzw6jC01041200t61F0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681118386&amp;ssig=TbvM6lvHVH&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OseBBAcNlx084wvz437G01041200iMgc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681118386&amp;ssig=OQfJdSVmlI&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4888520331034654&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
