            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#新版乳腺癌诊疗指南#发布，专家：#乳腺癌早发现早治疗尤其重要#】日前，中国临床肿瘤学会发布新版乳腺癌诊疗指南。乳腺癌是中国女性患病率和病死率最高...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E8%AF%8A%E7%96%97%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E8%AF%8A%E7%96%97%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#新版乳腺癌诊疗指南#</span></a>发布，专家：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E6%97%A9%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%E5%B0%A4%E5%85%B6%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B9%B3%E8%85%BA%E7%99%8C%E6%97%A9%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E6%97%A9%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%E5%B0%A4%E5%85%B6%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#乳腺癌早发现早治疗尤其重要#</span></a>】日前，中国临床肿瘤学会发布新版乳腺癌诊疗指南。乳腺癌是中国女性患病率和病死率最高的恶性肿瘤，每年新发病例约42万，很多患者确诊时已处中晚期，易发生局部复发和远处脏器转移。早期筛查发现、早诊断、早治疗尤其重要。（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4888558004273239" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hct890pmm7j60zk0k0q4z02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/nRLB3DgMlx084wFMEwwM01041200uZFr0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681118396&amp;ssig=NrVHPBELbO&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XaG5HkOWlx084wFLFGoM01041200f9L10E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681118396&amp;ssig=HvqA7DU7yq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><sou